title: JapanesePod101 jpod101 siterip (April 2018) japanese learning
description:
How can i use this?
Open index.html with your browser and go on from there.

What am I getting?
Collection of all japanesepod101 lessons in website format

Why are there no audio files?
This collection does not include audio files BUT you still have access to the audio files from jpod101 page. If you have internet conenction all the dialogs and videos should work without a problem. 

How many lessons are there?
Around 650

Does this have all the lessons?
No, the last time I checked some less known obscure lessons are missing. 

Can I access the lesson's PDFs?
No. You don't need them if you have the whole page. Besides some other torrent have them.

When was the snapshot made?
April 2018
